name">Fotografía de</span>&nbsp;<div class="author-name"><a href="https://www.latimes.com/people/robert-gauthier" aria-label="" data-click="standardBylineAuthorName">Robert Gauthier</a></div></div></div> </div>  <time datetime="2023-06-06T08:00:53.965Z" class="published-date"><span class="published-date-day">Jun. 6, 2023 </span><span class="published-time">1 AM PT </span></time></div>  <div class="page-actions"> <ps-actionbar class="action-bar"><ul class="action-bar-menu"><li><a class="action-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/dialog/share?app_id=125832154430708&display=popup&href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fespanol%2Fcalifornia%2Farticulo%2F2023-06-06%2Fcalifornia-retired-boxers-pension-plan-failing-to-deliver" target="_blank" data-social-service="facebook" data-social-trigger="actionBar"><svg class="icon facebook-icon"><use xlink:href="#mono-icon-facebook"></use></svg><span>Facebook</span></a></li><li><a class="action-link ActionLink" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fespanol%2Fcalifornia%2Farticulo%2F2023-06-06%2Fcalifornia-retired-boxers-pension-plan-failing-to-deliver&text=California%20cre%C3%B3%20la%20%C3%BAnica%20pensi%C3%B3n%20del%20pa%C3%ADs%20para%20boxeadores%20de%20edad%20avanzada.%20Pero%20muchos%20no%20la%20han%20recibido" target="_blank" data-social-service="twitter" data-social-trigger="actionBar"><svg><use xlink:href="#mono-icon-twitter"/></svg><span>Twitter</span></a></li><li><a class="action-link" data-dropdown-trigger href="#"><svg class="icon share-arrow-icon"><use xlink:href="#share-more-arrow"></use></svg><span>Show more sharing options</span></a></li></ul><div class="action-bar-dropdown"><div class="action-bar-dropdown-header"><span>Share</span><button class="button close-button" data-dropdown-close><svg class="icon close-icon"><use xlink:href="#close-x"></use></svg><span class="visually-hidden">Close extra sharing options</span></button></div><ul class="action-bar-dropdown-menu">  <li><a class="